search - find files by name
Executable: /bin/search.sh
Alias: search

DESCRIPTION
  Compatibility wrapper for the
  old ReMinux file search.
  Recursively searches for files
  whose path contains the given
  string fragment.

USAGE
  search <name> [start-path]

EXAMPLES
  search minux
  search .db

NOTES
  For Linux-style path walking,
  use 'find' instead.

SEE ALSO
  ls    - list a directory
  find  - Linux-style recursive
          file search
